  "description": "<p>Safe water is a simple pump away. This small portable water purifier is great when you're travelling light around questionable water sources. The two-stage filtration process removes 99.999% of viruses, bacteria, and protozoan cysts from the water and reduces chemicals and heavy metals, leaving you with purified, taste- and odour-free water.</p><ul><li>Hollow fibre technology uses polymer fibres to create a high-surface-area filter that allows water to flow quickly</li><li>Filter is effective against protozoa, bacteria, cysts, microplastics and viruses larger than 0.015 microns</li><li>Activated carbon disc traps heavy metals and industrial chemicals, and reduces odours and flavours</li><li>Hollow fibre filter purifies up to 5000L, activated carbon disc is effective up to 100L</li><li>Pump handle rotates for use with either hand</li><li>Includes 1.3m hose for drawing water from source and 0.5m hose for filling containers</li><li>Certified to NSF / ANSI P231 standard</li></ul>",
